    {
        "content": "<p>We just finished proving the commute with <code>extClass</code>.<br>\nNow we are only left to prove <code>flat base change commute with </code>Hom<code> when finitely presented</code> and <code>F</code> is exact implies <code>F.mapHomologicalComplex</code> is exact.</p>",
